  "3034530": {
    "name": "Zilar: Empire Of The Underground",
    "steam_appid": 3034530,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034530/extras/8cae4b9187a28da7f5a0dc11ccb0ccea.avif?t=1767963092\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034530/extras/154c354ba14949e7f0579cceeb79c3e9.webp?t=1767963092\" width=600 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>泽曼德夫的遗产：前往吉拉尔地下帝国的旅程</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Zilar: Empire of the Underground 讲述了游戏中的一本魔法书的故事，并邀请你踏上独特的冒险旅程。</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>我们的故事的主人公泽曼德夫，为了找回祖先大法师佐纳兰遗留下来的魔法王冠，踏上了危险的旅程。这个神秘的王冠被曾被认为只存在于传说中的耶克勒族及其领袖吉拉尔夺走了。为了阻止人类和耶克勒族之间的毁灭性战争重新爆发，并且为了夺回失去的遗产，泽曼德夫进入了吉拉尔的地下帝国。</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>在这段旅程中，你必须克服吉拉尔和耶克勒族设下的障碍，揭开过去的黑暗秘密，并为恢复你的遗产而战。你的勇气和智慧将是这场史诗任务的关键。</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034530/extras/91de3951fb6d687c7ab0281e89c43854.poster.avif?t=1767963092\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034530/extras/91de3951fb6d687c7ab0281e89c43854.webm?t=1767963092\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034530/extras/91de3951fb6d687c7ab0281e89c43854.mp4?t=1767963092\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034530/extras/15feebca4b6548b9043e0f587c37ac70.webp?t=1767963092\" width=600 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>模式与战略</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>与耶克勒族展开激烈的战斗，制定战术击败敌人。利用武器的三种不同模式，针对每种情况选择合适的战术，并将战场转为对你有利。</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034530/extras/84b56f994e5adfaa87cdb336403e9c40.poster.avif?t=1767963092\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034530/extras/84b56f994e5adfaa87cdb336403e9c40.webm?t=1767963092\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034530/extras/84b56f994e5adfaa87cdb336403e9c40.mp4?t=1767963092\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034530/extras/853f8c3e7cf398fe604fa7f1171973f9.webp?t=1767963092\" width=600 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>在地下跑酷中生存</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>在逃离吉拉尔的过程中，挑战地下帝国中艰难的跑酷关卡，测试你的速度和敏捷性。攀爬墙壁、跳跃平台，并利用环境避开敌人。每一步都需要小心，每个跑酷都会考验你的勇气。</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034530/extras/de531e1edd17269b1dbb4f92df99ab29.poster.avif?t=1767963092\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034530/extras/de531e1edd17269b1dbb4f92df99ab29.webm?t=1767963092\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034530/extras/de531e1edd17269b1dbb4f92df99ab29.mp4?t=1767963092\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034530/extras/b5a0ce5f51af4ba8a9ca6a9bcbd81a3c.webp?t=1767963092\" width=600 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>门后的秘密</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>解决复杂的谜题，揭开隐藏在封闭门后的秘密。一步步揭开过去的谜团，运用你的智慧向前推进。</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034530/extras/80bb5656b9ed98f27188bafb5bd28a0d.poster.avif?t=1767963092\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034530/extras/80bb5656b9ed98f27188bafb5bd28a0d.webm?t=1767963092\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034530/extras/80bb5656b9ed98f27188bafb5bd28a0d.mp4?t=1767963092\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034530/extras/893d5189ff83b7d113719fcb309d5e7a.avif?t=1767963092\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
